n't even come close to a full buffed level 60 cleric with a manastone as far as game impact goes. My level 60 cleric doesn't have the best gear because he is an alt, but even with what he has the length of time it takes for him to get from zero to fm is just plain silly. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4380>Qaman</a><BR>Sorcerer - Eternal Wrath<BR>Ayonae Ro</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarmok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Armok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<br>Need a log parsed?</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/12/02 10:18:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=927.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: thoughts</span><hr size=1> Bah, just add a 3 second stun if the manastone effect causes damage. Yes, this is biased toward wizards and their epic, but it would eliminate the evil cleric problem with manastones. I'd probably also make the manastone outdoor only. This makes more sense than making them old world only.<br> <p>"Evacuate? In our moment of triumph? I think you overestimate their chances!"<BR>Armok Komra (Triton)<BR>Sorcerer of Povar</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uwhizbangdustyboots.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Whizbang Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Gnomish Advocate</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/12/02 10:20:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=927.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.lby3.com/eq/whiz/flappy.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: thoughts</span><